Turn a fitdists Object into a Tidy Tibble

Source: R/coef.R
coef.fitdists.Rd

A wrapper on tidy.fitdists().

Usage

# S3 method for class 'fitdists'
coef(object, ...)

Arguments

object

The object.

...

Unused.

See also

tidy.fitdists()

Examples

fits <- ssd_fit_dists(ssddata::ccme_boron)
coef(fits)
#> # A tibble: 15 × 4
